Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,灰雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那黑雲沒有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為孤零零的飄在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被人們稱為殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,猿之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像臭雞蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你能聞到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,切 一直都是我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也說幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和我練習說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快點說點什麼吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是護送新娘的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,居然對喜慶的婚禮放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喜慶個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是被嫁給妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁給妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必須要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊去 我射你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的話跟我們說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我們對妖怪略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那邊有雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就出現在附近吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以為了不讓它吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次給妖怪準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它就老實回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,之後每次出現都會準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不準備的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就會被屠村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪也想要人類的新娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還要那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐說她們都被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂妖怪怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就是你姐姐被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要救出姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓妖怪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這時就該我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥幹掉過各式各樣的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那雲不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,當真?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不過不是免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不白做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要值錢的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在河裡撿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個的話還有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 成交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子 這是名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是個好名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快承認是好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說了不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我來救姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為了村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他們為了自己把你犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我自願來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓大家都被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓姐姐死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 那妖怪我們會收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就萬事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你們?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吃人的話肯定有嘴和肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就從那裡切開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥說交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在趕緊逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸的視線裡滿是火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍的雲也是妖怪的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之牆包圍的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次碰到什麼都看不到的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是你的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐不是我的親姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直是一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候爸爸和媽媽就病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有這座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說這不再是我的山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就把我趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那個住在山裡的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,長得像猴子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不記得自己的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要看著姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,飢餓和寒冷就都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,過去只有媽媽才對我這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個姐姐是不是曾經是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒功夫在這哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須替姐姐報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的工作都是有始有終的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一起解決掉那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在那片雲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥不能自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,必須靠我們自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那片雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是比原來更大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是那傢伙的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,蜈蚣脫皮之後會變得更大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,更大?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比現在還大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,得到新娘之後不是應該乖乖回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒準因為白天的事情生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它的弱點是日光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把它從雲裡拉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,應該就能打死它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話我有一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做吧猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,消滅蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐的復仇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是個大就強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的百足來我試試追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為了姐姐的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大的火也燒不掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在陽光下融化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 這樣也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥斬到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他剛才做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之牆遮擋住視線的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,憑藉著弓箭的聲音 確定了妖怪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 我說話的地方就是它的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他在呼喚多羅羅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我旁邊就是它的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這次總算結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,尾巴上還有一個頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你活著太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的鼻子恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著 這是你的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這石頭是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要不是這種石頭 是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那種亮晶晶的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有那些了 它們不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了你們 救我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你們接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在村子裡一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一個人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得好好想一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 名字是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得你真像個姐姐一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這個叫做氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才好像叫我「多羅羅」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字不錯吧
